FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776265866
OL,3,CPensioner who tied up and robbed 95-
OL,4,Cyear old woman jailed
OL,6,FMorrison left empty-handed from the
OL,7,Fproperty in Little Hulton, Salford, as
OL,8,Fhe was foiled by the arrival of the
OL,9,Fwoman's mobile hairdresser, Manchester
OL,10,FCrown Court heard.
OL,12,FHe targeted his vulnerable victim
OL,13,Fafter he visited her home previously
OL,14,Fwhen delivering medication as part of
OL,15,Fhis former job.
OL,17,FMorrison, who has no previous
OL,18,Fconvictions, retired aged 75 and was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with terminal kidney cancer
OL,20,Fin May 2024, the court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
