OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776265866
OL,3,CPensioner who tied up and robbed 95-
OL,4,Cyear old woman jailed
OL,6,FProsecutors said Morrison, of Worsley,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester, was regularly
OL,8,Fgambling at his local bookmaker's in
OL,9,Fthe months before the attack on 27
OL,10,FJanuary 2026.
OL,12,FThe court was told a psychiatric
OL,13,Freport had concluded Morrison was
OL,14,Fsuffering from a "depressive disorder"
OL,15,Fby the end of 2025.
OL,17,FIn a combination of "depression and
OL,18,Fdespair", he is said to have decided
OL,19,Fto end his life in February, while his
OL,20,Fpartner was away on a break.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
