OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776265866
OL,3,CPensioner who tied up and robbed 95-
OL,4,Cyear old woman jailed
OL,6,FIn a previous hearing, Morrison was
OL,7,Fsaid to have attempted to rob the
OL,8,Fwoman as a way to pay for his funeral.
OL,9,FHowever, at his sentencing on
OL,10,FWednesday 15 April the court heard he
OL,11,Fwas hoping to use the money to buy his
OL,12,Fpartner a new kitchen before taking
OL,13,Fhis own life
OL,15,FOn New Year's Day, he set up an online
OL,16,FGoFundMe appeal titled "Help to bury
OL,17,Fme" as he outlined his health problems.
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
