PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776265866
OL,3,CPensioner who tied up and robbed 95-
OL,4,Cyear old woman jailed
OL,6,FHe wrote: "More or less been told to
OL,7,Fgo in a corner and see my time out. I
OL,8,Fhave no money to cover funeral costs
OL,9,Fand other incidentals."
OL,11,FMr Clarke told the court: "He was
OL,12,Futterly selfish and self-centred ` for
OL,13,Fperhaps the first time in his life `
OL,14,Fin committing this offence.
OL,16,F"He is remorseful for what he has
OL,17,Fdone. It is submitted that no real
OL,18,Fharm was intended. The motivation for
OL,19,Fthis offending was altruistic rather
OL,20,Fthan malicious."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@WO]sD@[OUxD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
