PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776265866
OL,3,CPensioner who tied up and robbed 95-
OL,4,Cyear old woman jailed
OL,6,FIn a victim personal statement, his
OL,7,Fvictim told the court: "I thought I
OL,8,Fwas going to die."
OL,10,FShortly after, mobile hairdresser
OL,11,FMichaela Nelson arrived for her weekly
OL,12,Fappointment and let herself in.
OL,14,FMr Smith said: "Ms Nelson went into
OL,15,Fthe lounge and saw an old man sitting
OL,16,Fin front of the victim and assumed he
OL,17,Fwas a friend.
OL,19,F"(The victim) shouted at her to call
OL,20,Fthe police and she at first thought it
OL,21,Fwas a joke."
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@RO]vD@POU{D@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
