OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776265866
OL,3,CPensioner who tied up and robbed 95-
OL,4,Cyear old woman jailed
OL,6,FMorrison then held his hands up as if
OL,7,Fhe was going to grab the throat of the
OL,8,Fhairdresser, the court was told,
OL,9,Fbefore she ran away and he left the
OL,10,Fhouse.
OL,12,FPolice arrived shortly after and
OL,13,FMorrison was traced to his home
OL,14,Faddress by the movements of his
OL,15,FPeugeot, the court heard.
OL,17,FHe was charged on January 30 with a
OL,18,Fnumber of offences and was remanded
OL,19,Finto custody.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
