OL,3,CPensioner who tied up and robbed 95-
OL,4,Cyear old woman jailed
OL,6,FHe told the defendant: "You know there
OL,7,Fwill be an immediate sentence of
OL,8,Fcustody in this case. The only
OL,9,Fquestion is how long."
